ADDITIONAL USE RESTRICTIONS

This Software is a diagnostic and compliance-testing tool. The permission to
use, copy, modify, merge, publish, distribute, sublicense, and/or sell copies
granted above is conditional on the following restrictions. Any use that
violates these restrictions is not permitted under this License.

1. No circumvention of access restrictions.

   The Software MUST NOT be used, directly or indirectly, to build, operate,
   optimise, tune, calibrate, or evade detection by any system or service
   whose purpose is to circumvent lawful or unlawful restrictions on access
   to information resources, including but not limited to VPN, proxy, DPI
   bypass, traffic obfuscation, or censorship-circumvention tooling.

2. No surveillance of users.

   The Software MUST NOT be used, directly or indirectly, to collect,
   correlate, aggregate, profile, or otherwise process information about
   individual users, their identities, their devices, their network
   configuration, or the way in which they access or use the Internet, nor
   to feed any such information into law-enforcement, anti-fraud,
   telecommunications-regulator, or similar surveillance pipelines, whether
   run by the state, by a private party acting on behalf of the state, or
   by any other third party.

